.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, tea, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, manager, musician, pilot
City: london, liverpool, rome, prague
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, scooter, van
 1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the pilot##8
 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person traveling to prague##6
 8. the manager is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the musician is on the right of the freelancer##1
12. the manager is not the person traveling to london##6
13. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the manager##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite    | water   | tea        | iced-tea  |
| Job           | pilot     | manager | freelancer | musician  |
| City   | london | prague    | rome   | liverpool     |
| Transport     | van       | bus     | scooter    | quad-bike |

