 6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 7. the dutch is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 8. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
10. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the pakistani##8
11. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
12. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
14. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
